 The three destron silders took thier seats. They listened and looked at the 
thing Magmatron called the queen. They shook thier heads in understanding and 
eagerly awaited getting thier hands dirty in the feild of batttle. Galvatron 
waited for a reply to his comments. He continued to bounce his energy ball 
from his hand in a regulkar repeition. He thought to himself... "The 
preds..this will be a hard battle to win. Magmatron greatly under estimates 
his enemy. A quality that should not be over looked. The preds will have home 
advantage and see us comeing on thier screens....Unless......" He turned to 
Guiledart. "I need you to do something. Create a devise that can cloud us 
from the pred scanners. Try and do it quickly." Guiledart stood up and asked 
... "Where is your labratory where I may work?"

--part1_d0.10650cb4.279b3a16_boundary
